CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 10, 1961, pg. A6 reads: "Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 17, 1961, pg. 6A reads: "Grand Master Speaks - The Hon. Samuel T. Daniels, Grand Master of the Most Worshipful Prince Hall Grand Lodge of Maryland, gave a stirring address at the banquet held by the Grand Lodge, in Pittsburgh, recently."
TitMainTitle: Man wearing tuxedo with wide lapels, ribbon, and eyeglasses, standing at podium with microphone on large banquet table, during Prince Hall Grand Lodge banquet in the Penn Sheraton hotel
